Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.88,0:01:36.92,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,It's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.49,0:01:39.27,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,I'd better go get her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.80,0:01:49.17,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Now, who should we work on next?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.73,0:01:51.67,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll ask Kanade what she thinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.15,0:01:53.78,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.36,0:01:55.17,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Hinata!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.17,0:01:56.67,AB!_Naoi,Nao,0000,0000,0000,,Otonashi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.67,0:01:57.67,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Naoi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.30,0:02:01.72,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,What are {\i1}you{\i0} doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.72,0:02:03.81,AB!_Naoi,Nao,0000,0000,0000,,And where did you come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.18,0:02:07.54,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,So... did the two of you need something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.54,0:02:11.15,AB!_Naoi,Nao,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yes.  Where were you headed, Otonashi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.54,0:02:11.15,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yeah.  Where were you going, Otonashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.99,0:02:13.50,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,It's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.50,0:02:14.94,AB!_Naoi,Nao,0000,0000,0000,,It's none of {\i1}your{\i0} business.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.25,0:02:17.36,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,I've got business with Otonashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.36,0:02:20.36,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here to help him accomplish something!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.40,0:02:23.38,AB!_Naoi,Nao,0000,0000,0000,,But that would be {\i1}my{\i0} role.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.38,0:02:25.09,AB!_Naoi,Nao,0000,0000,0000,,You're not necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.09,0:02:26.97,AB!_Naoi,Nao,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.37,0:02:31.92,AB!_Naoi,Nao,0000,0000,0000,,Good.  Look into my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.27,0:02:34.71,AB!_Naoi,Nao,0000,0000,0000,,You're a roll of toilet paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.71,0:02:38.30,AB!_Naoi,Nao,0000,0000,0000,,Realize how swiftly toilet paper is washed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.30,0:02:40.59,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now, cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.26,0:02:42.51,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, Hinata!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.18,0:02:45.26,AB!_Naoi,Nao,0000,0000,0000,,Please allow me to assist you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.47,0:02:49.18,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Do you guys even know what I'm trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.18,0:02:50.27,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.57,0:02:52.15,AB!_Naoi,Nao,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.60,0:02:54.82,AB!_Naoi,Nao,0000,0000,0000,,You're trying to obliterate us one by one, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.82,0:02:57.32,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Coming from you, it sounds more like a crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.33,0:03:02.31,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,If you think about it, Naoi,\Nyou don't have any regrets now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.31,0:03:05.24,AB!_Naoi,Nao,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be with you.  And besides,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.24,0:03:07.67,AB!_Naoi,Nao,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be obliterated before him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.67,0:03:09.66,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stay behind for a reason like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.97,0:03:11.93,AB!_Naoi,Nao,0000,0000,0000,,Then what am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.93,0:03:12.96,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Be obliterated.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.96,0:03:14.67,AB!_Naoi,Nao,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody asked {\i1}you{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.29,0:03:18.55,AB!_Naoi,Nao,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Otonashi-san, you need a partner, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.55,0:03:21.61,AB!_Naoi,Nao,0000,0000,0000,,Please use me, Otonashi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.84,0:03:24.05,AB!_Naoi,Nao,0000,0000,0000,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.30,0:03:28.68,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?  Did you do something again?! {Mata nanika shitanoka?} {ep10}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.89,0:03:30.31,AB!_Naoi,Nao,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.48,0:03:31.52,AB!_Naoi,Nao,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't done-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.23,0:03:35.09,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.09,0:03:36.86,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Is it an enemy?  Can we shoot it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.08,0:03:39.03,AB!_Naoi,Nao,0000,0000,0000,,It's invading...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.60,0:03:41.82,AB!_Naoi,Nao,0000,0000,0000,,Something's invading me, Otonashi-san! {nanika haitte kimasu, Otonashi-san!} {ep10}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.14,AB!_Naoi,Nao,0000,0000,0000,,{physically or figuratively, like into the mind, is not clear}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.99,0:03:42.61,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!! {Kuso!!} {ep10}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.95,0:03:50.75,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Hinata!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.58,0:03:54.33,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Can this thing die?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.80,0:04:02.93,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Did we get rid of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.05,0:04:06.60,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.96,0:04:12.00,AB!_Yusa,Yus,0000,0000,0000,,Target intercepted by Hinata-san and Otonashi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.00,0:04:13.90,AB!_Yusa,Yus,0000,0000,0000,,It's been exterminated.  No casualties.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.80,0:04:16.78,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,A second one showed up, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.78,0:04:20.72,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be natural to assume it's one of Tenshi's new skills, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.72,0:04:21.99,AB!_Yusa,Yus,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't sound right to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.22,0:04:23.40,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,No, it doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.27,0:04:27.61,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,This is an edict to all Battlefront members:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.61,0:04:29.33,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,No one is permitted to travel alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.61,0:04:31.96,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Move together with a minimum of one other person at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.41,0:04:35.46,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,The Shadows will be considered an enemy unrelated to Tenshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.20,0:04:38.76,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Be sure to maintain high alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.76,0:04:39.96,AB!_Yusa,Yus,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.59,0:04:41.76,AB!_Yusa,Yus,0000,0000,0000,,And you, Yurippe-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.78,0:04:45.13,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,I'm headed out to eliminate some possibilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.96,0:04:51.54,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Student Council President, Tachibana Kanade-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.52,0:04:54.31,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Please report to the Student Council room immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.31,0:04:55.23,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I repeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.60,0:04:58.02,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Student Council President, Tachibana Kanade-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.02,0:05:00.65,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Please report to the Student Council room immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.02,0:04:54.31,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that's Yurippe, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.31,0:04:55.60,AB!_Naoi,Nao,0000,0000,0000,,What is this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.60,0:04:59.37,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Crap.  She might hear from her what we're trying to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.37,0:05:00.66,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.23,0:05:02.11,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.11,0:05:02.73,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.60,0:05:07.11,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.61,0:05:09.04,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Let us listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.04,0:05:13.60,AB!_Naoi,Nao,0000,0000,0000,,I, as the ex-deputy president and\Ncurrent vice president, permit them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.60,0:05:15.37,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Why is this under your jurisdiction?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.62,0:05:17.37,AB!_Naoi,Nao,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Student Council room.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.05,0:05:20.04,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.63,0:05:24.38,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,So?  What are these Shadows?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.60,0:05:25.50,AB!_Angel,Ten,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.88,0:05:28.13,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't program them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.39,0:05:29.14,AB!_Angel,Ten,0000,0000,0000,,I did not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.45,0:05:32.03,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Then it could be a bug.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.03,0:05:34.33,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,When was the last time you did any programming?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.33,0:05:35.35,AB!_Angel,Ten,0000,0000,0000,,The day before yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.35,0:05:37.14,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Timing-wise, it's a perfect match.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.68,0:05:40.02,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be sending people into your room, understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.75,0:05:43.38,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Takeyama-kun, it's your show.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.38,0:05:44.12,AB!_Takeyama,Chr,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.12,0:05:45.35,AB!_Takeyama,Chr,0000,0000,0000,,And call me Chr-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.35,0:05:47.14,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,So, what sort of program did you write?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.14,0:05:47.87,AB!_Angel,Ten,0000,0000,0000,,Wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.87,0:05:49.97,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,"Wings"?  You added wings?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.97,0:05:51.28,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,So you can fly?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.46,0:05:53.03,AB!_Angel,Ten,0000,0000,0000,,No.  They're for decoration.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.99,0:05:54.79,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,"Decoration"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.98,0:05:56.55,AB!_Angel,Ten,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.  Decoration.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.55,0:05:57.41,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.41,0:06:00.28,AB!_Angel,Ten,0000,0000,0000,,Because I was told that I would look more like an angel that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.28,0:06:02.63,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,"Told"?  Who told you that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.47,0:06:04.42,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Crap...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.42,0:06:05.92,AB!_Naoi,Nao,0000,0000,0000,,That would be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.63,0:06:10.93,AB!_Naoi,Nao,0000,0000,0000,,I felt it would add to her supremacy as president, so I,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.93,0:06:14.14,AB!_Naoi,Nao,0000,0000,0000,,the ex-deputy president and\Ncurrent vice president, suggested it to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.14,0:06:17.06,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,A president with wings looks supreme, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.06,0:06:17.81,AB!_Naoi,Nao,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.81,0:06:20.08,AB!_Naoi,Nao,0000,0000,0000,,Wings for the president.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.08,0:06:21.56,AB!_Naoi,Nao,0000,0000,0000,,I believe it's fitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.44,0:06:28.32,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,What a dumbass.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.70,0:06:31.28,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, you're being pretty obedient.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.28,0:06:33.70,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,You don't seem heartless at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.95,0:06:36.20,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,No different from how you were before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.29,0:06:37.75,AB!_Naoi,Nao,0000,0000,0000,,No, she is heartless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.75,0:06:40.42,AB!_Naoi,Nao,0000,0000,0000,,As the vice president, I get stabbed by her each day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.42,0:06:41.92,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Um, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.92,0:06:45.17,AB!_Naoi,Nao,0000,0000,0000,,When she's in a bad mood, she stabs anything near her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.17,0:06:49.63,AB!_Naoi,Nao,0000,0000,0000,,As the vice president, I'm often nearby, so as a result, I'm stabbed often.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.63,0:06:52.34,AB!_Naoi,Nao,0000,0000,0000,,I was stabbed this morning, actually,\Nand my intestines were hanging out for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.09,0:06:55.68,AB!_Naoi,Nao,0000,0000,0000,,But right now, she seems to be in a good mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.85,0:06:58.68,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,What a dumbass.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.77,0:07:02.73,AB!_Takeyama,Chr,0000,0000,0000,,Do you copy?  Please respond.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.70,0:07:05.73,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,How is it, Takeyama-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.23,0:07:08.15,AB!_Takeyama,Chr,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't find any bugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.15,0:07:12.36,AB!_Takeyama,Chr,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, this program is for decoration only, so it's a relatively simple one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.74,0:07:16.49,AB!_Takeyama,Chr,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't possibly produce a bug with a mind of its own that attacks people.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:19.41,AB!_Takeyama,Chr,0000,0000,0000,,Also, please call me Chr-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.66,0:07:20.00,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,What about the other programs?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.79,0:07:24.38,AB!_Takeyama,Chr,0000,0000,0000,,There's Overdrive in passive mode.  Hand Sonic in active mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.79,0:07:28.38,AB!_Takeyama,Chr,0000,0000,0000,,All of them are just the same as before.  Although their forms look different.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.38,0:07:29.01,AB!_Takeyama,Chr,0000,0000,0000,,What would you like to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.24,0:07:32.63,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Is she going to make him delete it? {Orig. Yuri}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.63,0:07:34.68,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,She'd have to write it again from scratch. {Orig Yuri}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.76,0:07:38.01,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you just hear that gunshot?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.97,0:07:41.06,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,What gunshot?  I didn't hear any-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.02,0:07:42.77,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming from outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.48,0:07:47.52,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Look!  Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.86,0:07:49.19,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,It's those monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.53,0:07:51.36,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,My God!  Look at how many of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.14,0:07:53.35,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Kanade!  Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.57,0:08:10.30,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Yurippe!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.97,0:08:16.50,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.50,0:08:17.65,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.64,0:08:18.39,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.40,0:08:19.24,AB!_Naoi,Nao,0000,0000,0000,,Otonashi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.15,0:08:30.45,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Yuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.45,0:08:31.11,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Otonashi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.11,0:08:32.49,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.03,0:08:33.99,AB!_Naoi,Nao,0000,0000,0000,,Hit the deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.86,0:08:36.57,AB!_Noda,Nod,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need help! {Kasei nado Iran}{ep10}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.57,0:08:38.07,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.23,0:08:45.59,AB!_Shiina,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,How unwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.00,0:08:49.00,AB!_T.K.,TK,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!   Dancing in the shadow! {ep10}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.74,0:08:55.26,AB!_T.K.,TK,0000,0000,0000,,I kiss you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.77,0:09:09.52,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,I'd hate to get hit with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.40,0:09:15.45,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to cut us down with them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.78,0:09:17.16,AB!_Noda,Nod,0000,0000,0000,,That's just part of my plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.17,0:09:18.70,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Take it out next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.70,0:09:20.95,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Stop horsing around and support each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.40,0:09:27.29,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.78,0:09:35.66,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Is everyone safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.67,0:09:39.64,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.  What were they?  Are they monsters?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.64,0:09:43.64,AB!_Noda,Nod,0000,0000,0000,,Those freaky creatures never existed in this world before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.64,0:09:45.31,AB!_Shiina,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Is this some sort of nightmare? {Kore ha akmu ka?} {ep10}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.31,0:09:47.60,AB!_T.K.,TK,0000,0000,0000,,A carnival of nightmares.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.60,0:09:50.23,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we've been in this world for too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.23,0:09:51.52,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.52,0:09:56.65,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,You've seen invincible monsters in games meant to prevent one from being able to play said game forever, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.65,0:09:58.04,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,That's not funny at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.57,0:09:59.53,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.36,0:10:01.78,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,she's acting as our ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.53,0:10:05.04,AB!_Fujimaki,Fuj,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!  Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.35,0:10:06.57,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Fujimaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.37,0:10:08.58,AB!_Fujimaki,Fuj,0000,0000,0000,,We got a problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.58,0:10:13.54,AB!_Fujimaki,Fuj,0000,0000,0000,,Takamatsu!  Takamatsu lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.24,0:10:23.68,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Those are his glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.88,0:10:28.43,AB!_Ooyama,Ooy,0000,0000,0000,,I saw it.  That Shadow ate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.43,0:10:29.81,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,"Ate"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.81,0:10:34.94,AB!_Ooyama,Ooy,0000,0000,0000,,By the time I saw him, he was already completely covered by a Shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.36,0:10:37.86,AB!_Ooyama,Ooy,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to save him, too! {Boku mo tasuke youto shitanda}{ep10}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.87,0:10:40.07,AB!_Ooyama,Ooy,0000,0000,0000,,But I couldn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.40,0:10:43.41,AB!_Ooyama,Ooy,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, his glasses fell...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.41,0:10:45.66,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Who'd have thought he'd drop his glasses... {Aitsu ga megane wo otosu nante...}{ep10}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.66,0:10:47.91,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,How unreal.  And then what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.91,0:10:50.75,AB!_Ooyama,Ooy,0000,0000,0000,,He was sucked into the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.76,0:10:51.71,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,"The ground"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.04,0:10:53.46,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,This is too much of an irregularity... {Irregular sugiru}{ep10}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.55,0:10:59.29,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?  A third party that's not related to any of us is starting to take action.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.88,0:11:01.76,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly is going on? {naniga okiterunda?} {ep10}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.80,0:11:07.89,AB!_Noda,Nod,0000,0000,0000,,I found Takamatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.81,0:11:09.70,AB!_Ooyama,Ooy,0000,0000,0000,,Takamatsu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.19,0:11:09.98,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Takamatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.27,0:11:13.48,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?  Everyone was worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.13,0:11:16.80,AB!_Takamatsu,Tak,0000,0000,0000,,"Worried"?  Over what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.77,0:11:20.61,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,"Over what"?  You got eaten by that shadow monster! {making is lower case here since "shadow" is used as adjective, not as noun.}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.20,0:11:23.57,AB!_Takamatsu,Tak,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand what you're speaking of.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.57,0:11:26.09,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he doesn't realize what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.09,0:11:27.88,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,You got eaten by a Shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.88,0:11:30.66,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,And then you got sucked into the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.66,0:11:32.37,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.37,0:11:33.79,AB!_Takamatsu,Tak,0000,0000,0000,,What did I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.25,0:11:37.67,AB!_Takamatsu,Tak,0000,0000,0000,,I woke up at the dorm and came to school like I do any other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.67,0:11:39.44,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,"Came to school"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.44,0:11:42.63,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,You're here to attend class in that uniform?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.63,0:11:43.55,AB!_Takamatsu,Tak,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.55,0:11:45.89,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be obliterated!  Don't you get that?! {Kieruzo!} {ep10}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.47,0:11:47.68,AB!_Takamatsu,Tak,0000,0000,0000,,"Obliterated"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.68,0:11:49.47,AB!_Takamatsu,Tak,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "obliterated"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.98,0:11:55.40,AB!_Fujimaki,Fuj,0000,0000,0000,,Holy crap.  He's gone bonkers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.87,0:11:57.77,AB!_Fujimaki,Fuj,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he was to begin with, but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.49,0:11:59.55,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Takamatsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.55,0:12:01.36,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough, Hinata-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.36,0:12:02.74,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Enough of {\i1}what{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.74,0:12:05.24,AB!_Takamatsu,Tak,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry to say this, but you're interrupting class.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.25,0:12:06.03,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.03,0:12:07.53,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,You sure we wanna leave him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.74,0:12:08.91,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be obliterated!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.93,0:12:09.80,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Just come.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.78,0:12:12.88,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Ooyama-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.84,0:12:22.21,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,His reactions just now speak volumes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.21,0:12:24.13,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,I've grasped what's happened to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.97,0:12:27.93,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,He's turned into an NPC.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.43,0:12:33.06,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hold on!  What does that mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.06,0:12:34.19,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,This is too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.19,0:12:37.27,AB!_Ooyama,Ooy,0000,0000,0000,,If he's an NPC, then he doesn't have a soul anymore, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.27,0:12:40.19,AB!_Ooyama,Ooy,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, where did his soul go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.44,0:12:42.69,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe that's what was eaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.69,0:12:45.11,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.11,0:12:51.37,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,You mean he's even lost the chance to be obliterated and has to take classes here forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.37,0:12:53.07,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.07,0:12:57.07,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,That's...  That's even worse than dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.08,0:13:01.09,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,So, really forever?  He's locked in here {\i1}forever{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.09,0:13:02.09,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,What kinda sick joke is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.21,0:13:03.05,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.34,0:13:05.47,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,That's just screwed up...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.18,0:13:11.43,AB!_Noda,Nod,0000,0000,0000,,So something like this is possible in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.72,0:13:15.64,AB!_Fujimaki,Fuj,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be better gettin' obliterated by Tenshi. {Tenshi ni kesarechimatta houga mada mashi ja ne-kayo}{ep10}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.64,0:13:18.56,AB!_Shiina,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, it looks like the Shadow is multiplying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:21.44,AB!_Ooyama,Ooy,0000,0000,0000,,What do we need to do, Yurippe?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.95,0:13:34.58,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Something strange is starting to happen in this world. {Kono sekai ni ihen ga okihajimete iru} {ep10}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.75,0:13:37.16,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,To begin with, the appearance of enemies other than Tenshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.16,0:13:39.54,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,For lack of originality, we call them Shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.88,0:13:44.38,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike Tenshi, they appear suddenly and attack us at random.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.38,0:13:50.89,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Once eaten by a Shadow, you lose your soul and are turned into an NPC that attends class every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.22,0:13:55.10,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Currently, they are multiplying without limit.  The cause is unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.10,0:13:57.31,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,We have no countermeasure at this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.31,0:14:02.77,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,As Yusa-san said earlier, you need to protect each other by staying in groups.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.32,0:14:10.28,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Now, in the midst of this crisis, we have people developing a different ideal within the Battlefront,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.57,0:14:13.78,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,and they are trying to lead the organization in a new direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.78,0:14:19.71,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,That direction could lead to a countermeasure to the crisis we're facing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.73,0:14:24.13,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,So, as the representative of that faction, Otonashi-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.13,0:14:27.05,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,could you share your ideal with all of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.47,0:14:32.09,AB!_Naoi,Nao,0000,0000,0000,,She knew about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.09,0:14:33.01,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Go on up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.24,0:14:55.08,AB!_Anon,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,Screw you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.33,0:14:56.95,AB!_Anon,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,That's all baseless!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.95,0:14:59.08,AB!_Anon,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't be true!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.08,0:15:01.79,AB!_Anon,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!  Nothing like that could exist here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.79,0:15:03.29,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Well it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.17,0:15:07.18,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Yui found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.26,0:15:12.18,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Even I died as a worthless husk of a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.76,0:15:15.93,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,But in this world, I was able to give her purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.68,0:15:17.89,AB!_Naoi,Nao,0000,0000,0000,,The same applies to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.93,0:15:20.43,AB!_Naoi,Nao,0000,0000,0000,,I am God...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.52,0:15:27.69,AB!_Naoi,Nao,0000,0000,0000,,But Otonashi-san managed to help me regain my human heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.23,0:15:32.45,AB!_Naoi,Nao,0000,0000,0000,,all with a single pat on the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.49,0:15:36.78,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,It's entirely your choice which path you take.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.78,0:15:39.70,AB!_Anon,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?  What will you do, Yurippe?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.87,0:15:43.50,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Me?  I've always done what I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.50,0:15:45.46,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,I can't protect you all, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.96,0:15:48.17,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll continue to do what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.40,0:15:55.05,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.05,0:15:56.93,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,All of you should give it much thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.39,0:15:59.18,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.  Dismissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.56,0:16:02.77,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,You have a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.29,0:16:07.61,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want, Yuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.11,0:16:10.86,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Make her work to intercept the Shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.86,0:16:12.78,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Kanade?  Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.78,0:16:18.08,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,She's more suited for fighting without thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.08,0:16:19.37,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,At least, based on what I saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.39,0:16:22.25,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,So you were watching...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.58,0:16:25.62,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Man, we can't deceive Yurippe's eyes, can we?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.62,0:16:29.75,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,But Kanade is on our side.  She should stay with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.00,0:16:33.30,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,So are all the other members.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.30,0:16:36.47,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,To protect them, we need her strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.14,0:16:42.22,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,We need her great strength, which she used to fight against the Battlefront for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.60,0:16:45.98,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.  It's a fitting role for her as an angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.98,0:16:48.36,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,She's not an angel, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.82,0:16:51.65,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!  What did you just say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.65,0:16:53.61,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,I said she's not an angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.15,0:16:56.32,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,She's a human just like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.32,0:16:57.87,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,You never realized?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.03,0:17:02.87,AB!_Naoi,Nao,0000,0000,0000,,God is omniscient.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.16,0:17:04.87,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,You're shaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.29,0:17:07.62,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're not an angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.79,0:17:10.96,AB!_Angel,Ten,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm not an angel."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.96,0:17:14.76,AB!_Angel,Ten,0000,0000,0000,,I'm certain I said that to you when we first met.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.26,0:17:18.43,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She was calling you an angel or whatnot.{\i0}{ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.05,0:17:21.05,AB!_Angel,Ten,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm not an angel.{\i0} {ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.53,0:17:23.64,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,She did!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.64,0:17:25.60,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, a lot's happened since, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.60,0:17:27.14,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,This is all your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.14,0:17:29.35,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, why is Kanade here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.35,0:17:31.90,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Why wasn't she obliterated for being the Student Council President?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.15,0:17:35.40,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,She must have her reasons for staying here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.78,0:17:38.16,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.49,0:17:43.04,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Then just like us, she has some kind of regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.66,0:17:45.95,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,We'll need to take care of that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.95,0:17:46.71,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.29,0:17:52.88,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,So, Yuri...  What will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.90,0:17:55.00,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I want to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.01,0:17:56.80,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to fight against the Shadows?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.80,0:17:57.72,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,If it's necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.93,0:17:59.22,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous to go alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.58,0:18:04.35,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,What can I do?  I gave everyone the freedom to choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.59,0:18:06.81,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure some will follow you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.81,0:18:09.17,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,They need time to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.14,0:18:10.81,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,It's an important decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.81,0:18:13.39,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... it is, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.40,0:18:18.70,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,If everyone's been obliterated and has safely left this world by the time I return,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.70,0:18:21.49,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,then I'll believe you did what you had to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.49,0:18:23.45,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that!  I'll be waiting! {Ore ha matte iru!} {ep10}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.78,0:18:27.70,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be an idiot.  If you wait alone, the Shadows will get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.04,0:18:32.25,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,You should leave this world before that happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.63,0:18:34.54,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.54,0:18:36.34,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,No, we will worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.34,0:18:37.21,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Hinata-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.46,0:18:39.33,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.80,0:18:42.26,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,This Battlefront started with just us two.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.91,0:18:45.60,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,We spent lots of time together, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.60,0:18:48.00,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,So we'll end it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.00,0:18:50.09,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,I won't leave without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.75,0:18:53.06,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,You're such an idiot, as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.06,0:18:55.77,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Sentiment won't solve a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.65,0:18:58.82,AB!_Anon,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy!  Enemy raid!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.76,0:19:01.24,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Kanade-chan, please go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.70,0:19:03.99,AB!_Angel,Ten,0000,0000,0000,,Hand Sonic: Version 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.35,0:19:10.24,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we'll meet again if we can. {ja, mata aetara aimashou.} {ep10}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.24,0:19:11.21,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Yurippe! {ep10}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.13,0:19:16.55,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,What a terrible nickname.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.09,0:19:20.67,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,But... maybe that's why people flocked to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.63,0:19:22.59,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.17,0:20:47.72,AB!_Takeyama,Chr,0000,0000,0070,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.05,0:20:50.28,AB!_Takeyama,Chr,0000,0000,0070,,I'll stop it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.96,0:21:05.20,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,That transformation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.57,0:21:15.79,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Just like that boy, if an NPC's program can be rewritten...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.29,0:21:23.63,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,That means there's a person using that software to change NPCs into Shadows, setting them to attack us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.63,0:21:29.68,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone playing God for this world and using this to screw around with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.26,0:21:33.35,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Wherever this person is, there must also be countless computers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.85,0:21:36.85,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,And if so, there's only one possible place.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.82,0:21:55.12,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Checkmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.12,0:21:56.54,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your hands in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.54,0:21:58.46,AB!_Anon,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?  What's this now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.79,0:22:00.67,AB!_Anon,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,"Checkmate"?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.67,0:22:02.71,AB!_Anon,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Were you playing chess?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.95,0:22:04.51,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,He's the one behind all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.13,0:22:09.88,AB!_Anon,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The world requires computers for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.88,0:22:12.43,AB!_Anon,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Playing an analog game is good, too, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.43,0:22:15.64,AB!_Anon,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Despite being young, you have a good hobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.85,0:22:16.77,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Wait right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.97,0:22:19.15,AB!_Anon,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.15,0:22:20.61,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,What were you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.61,0:22:21.77,AB!_Anon,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.98,0:22:22.89,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.89,0:22:25.81,AB!_Anon,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I was setting up a new computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.81,0:22:26.87,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,For what reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.99,0:22:30.78,AB!_Anon,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's because computers are valuable, but they often get stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.78,0:22:33.41,AB!_Anon,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,If they go missing, I need to replace them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.41,0:22:35.26,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any idea who takes them?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.26,0:22:37.72,AB!_Anon,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Not at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.85,0:22:41.28,AB!_Anon,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,May I go now?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.10,0:22:43.14,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.54,0:22:45.00,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,My apologies for keeping you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.32,0:23:08.65,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,There's no mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.03,0:23:13.53,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,That burglar is playing the role of God in this world right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.74,0:23:18.58,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Using the PCs they've stolen, they're starting to tamper with the NPCs.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.58,0:23:20.58,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,But how should I capture them?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.79,0:23:23.83,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.83,0:23:26.17,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,The Shadows are multiplying this very moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.92,0:23:30.67,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's easy to say "steal,"\Nbut these aren't easily transportable.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.38,0:23:35.51,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Do they sneak in at night and carry them out on a dolly?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.01,0:23:37.67,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe out the window?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.35,0:23:58.67,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.42,0:24:07.25,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,What?  No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.76,0:24:12.76,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Not the Guild again!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.97,0:24:17.85,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to break through! {toppa suruzo!}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.68,0:24:19.41,AB!_T.K.,TK,0000,0000,0000,,Knockin' on heaven's door.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.80,0:24:19.39,AB!_Matsushita,Nod,0000,0000,0000,,What is this world? {Nanda kono sekai ha?}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.60,0:24:20.47,AB!_Ooyama,Ooy,0000,0000,0000,,I thought even God would be surprised! {Kami-sama for bikkiru gyouten kanatte}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.68,0:24:23.23,AB!_Fujimaki,Fuj,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think anyone'd notice even if you disappeared right now! {Kono mama inaku nattemo, daremo kidukanasou dakarana!}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.01,0:24:20.26,AB!_Cha,Cha,0000,0000,0000,,So the war's... going to end... {Tatakai ga owaru noka...}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.43,0:24:21.36,AB!_Yuri,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost! {Kiero!}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.89,0:24:22.68,AB!_Naoi,Nao,0000,0000,0000,,Disappear pitifully, just like toilet paper! {toilet paper no youni mijime ni kiero}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.30,0:24:22.71,AB!_Noda,Nod,0000,0000,0000,,I only move when it helps Yurippe! {Ore ga ugoku no ha Yurippe no tasuke ni naru toki dakeda!}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.68,0:24:25.19,AB!_Shiina,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,One hundred...  Just think, we have reinforcements. {Hyakunin...  Senryoku ga fueta to omoe}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.23,0:24:25.14,AB!_Hisako,His,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be a band next time, too!  {Tsugi mo band yaruyo}  {Timer : ???}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.19,0:24:25.69,AB!_PlotDevice,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I am amazed you made it this far. {Yoku tadori tsuke mashita ne}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.75,0:24:25.46,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Reach out! {te wo nobase!}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.69,0:24:28.52,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm obliterated from this place...  can I redo my life?
